//
// Shared Explorer-facing application icon for DisplayXR executables.
//
// ID 1 is the lowest icon resource ID in the module, so Explorer / the
// shell pick it as the file icon. The asset is the white DisplayXR mark
// composited on a dark rounded tile, so it stays legible on both light
// and dark Explorer themes (a bare black or white mark disappears on one
// of the two). Theme-aware contexts (e.g. the service tray) instead load
// their white/black flat variants by explicit resource ID.

1 ICON "../../../../assets/displayxr_app.ico"
